nodes.text: The Iktotch blockade was a blockade in the Imperial Navy that operated at the moon Iktotch during the Imperial Era.

The Iktotch blockade was first introduced in Nexus of Power, albeit only mentioned by its official name, a sourcebook for Fantasy Flight Games' Star Wars: Force and Destiny roleplaying game that was released on March 17, 2016, and contains elements from both Canon and Legends continuities, and primarily focuses on vergences, locations that have a connection to the Force.
